---
---

<section class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy-light/50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-coral font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who is this for?</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-14">
      Built for people who care where their data lives.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Persona 1: Community managers -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-coral/20 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Community managers</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Run a Discord server or Telegram group. Comis answers FAQs, moderates conversations, summarizes threads, and remembers regulars - across every channel you operate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Persona 2: Small business owners -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Small business owners</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Triage WhatsApp messages, draft email replies, watch your inbox for vendor updates. A team of agents does the front-line work while you focus on customers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Persona 3: Developers -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Developers</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your AI assistant, in your pocket, with real tools and memory that persists. Research, code, automate - all from the messaging apps you already use, on infra you control.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Persona 4: Teams -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-muted-light" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Teams &amp; startups</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          A fleet of specialized agents - research, code review, ops - coordinated through DAG pipelines with isolated budgets, tool policies, and audit trails.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
